The issue of a new driver's license lasts 20 days.
But it is possible to apply for the exhibition with a shortened period of five days.
In this case, however, the driver must add 500 kroner.
Motorists who fail to make the required exchange by the end of the year and drive without a valid driver's license are facing a fine from January onwards.
The evildoer pays a maximum of 2000 kroner.
However, the police can also put an end to the transgression with a warning.
In the event of an infringement, the penalty may rise to 2500 kroner.
